Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

###

### [6.2] Login with non-existent email → should return 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ghost@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### [6.3] Report issue without token → should return 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/issues
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Unauthorized issue",
  "description": "This should fail",
  "category": "Garbage",
  "latitude": 24.8607,
  "longitude": 67.0011
}

###

### [6.4] Report issue missing required fields → should return 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/issues
Authorization: Bearer {{citizenToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Missing fields issue"
}

###

### [6.5] Upvote same issue twice → should return 400 (already upvoted)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/upvotes
Authorization: Bearer {{citizenToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "issueId": "{{issueId2}}" }

###

### [6.6] Admin update with invalid status → should return 400
